stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle
  Idle --> Active: EnterPickerMode
  Active --> Hovering: mousemove
  Hovering --> Hovering: mousemove (update overlay)
  Hovering --> Selecting: contextmenu (right-click)
  Hovering --> Cancelling: Escape
  Hovering --> Cancelling: ExitPickerMode
  Active --> Cancelling: Escape
  Selecting --> Idle: export ok (StatusUpdate=Success)
  Selecting --> Idle: export error (StatusUpdate=Error)
  Cancelling --> Idle
  Idle --> [*]
